# koa-modern-router

[![NPM version](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/koa-modern-router.svg?style=flat)](https://npmjs.org/package/koa-modern-router)

Simple and modern router middleware for Koa [koa](https://github.com/koajs/koa), maintained by someone who relies on Koa every day.

## IMPORTANT

It is not my goal to simply maintain koa-router under a new name. There may be breaking changes in the future. If you just want to keep using koa-router safely, you should `npm i koa-router@7.4.0` and always use `npm ci` and
`save-exact=true` in your `.npmrc`.`

* Express-style routing using `app.get`, `app.put`, `app.post`, etc.
* Named URL parameters.
* Named routes with URL generation.
* Responds to `OPTIONS` requests with allowed methods.
* Support for `405 Method Not Allowed` and `501 Not Implemented`.
* Multiple route middleware.
* Multiple routers.
* Nestable routers.
* ES7 async/await support.

